data.description:
New Carpet though out, this 4 bedroom 2 bath home has an Open floor Plan that features a nice size living room that
flows into a well designed kitchen. The Kitchen features an island and plenty of cabinets and counter space. Enhanced w/granite . All Stainless-Steel Appliances
Microwave, and Dishwasher.  The master suite has a private bath with double vanity sinks and a roomy walk-in closet. This desirable plan
also comes complete with a 2-car garage. Wood faux blinds and remote controlled ceiling fans t/o. Backyard fully landscaped with rock.  great area to enjoy a BBQ.
